Package gameWorld.rooms

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BossRoom
    A BossRoom is a Room, that upon being defeated allows the Hero to move floors.
    MobRoom
    A MobRoom is a Room, that holds a random amount of Monsters.
    Room
    A room, is a place that the Hero can move , and that is surrounded by some Wall.
    ShopRoom
    A ShopRoom is a Room, that holds three items with a set price.
    SpawnRoom
    A SpawnRoom is a Room, that is safe, as it doesn't have any monster or harmful traps.
